SYNOPSIS:
Second-year high school student Kindaichi Hajime is the grandson of famous detective Kindaichi Kousuke. He is usually a frivolous person, but when cases occur, he solves them with deductive powers inherited from his grandfather. Kindaichi belongs to the Mystery Investigations Club and together with his childhood friend and classmate Nanase Miyuki, and junior Saki Ryuji, they encounter various difficult cases.
